Let us welcome our loved ones home this Halloween night.
This calavera is Josefina. She was 18 when she died. She was a bright and cheerful girl who loved flowers and romantic tales. She was in love with Juan, who lives next door. Young, dreamy, and lovely, that is how her friends and family remember her in their hearts.
